{"tid":412139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人網上一句:「跟我加入ISIS」 被判監9個月","createTime":"2017-09-24T11:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T15:10:21.000Z","uid":53705,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb7814630ecae3b5e780f51081fcd4fa4891c1b","tid":412139,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170922/bkncn-20170922161158345-0922_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170922%2Fbkncn-20170922161158345-0922_05011_001.html&d=yVtyxoXahcwQYUUTYm3W6aNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=3418ba6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170922/bkncn-20170922161158345-0922_05011_001.html</a><br />\n事發去年9月4日晚上，張強在北京昌平區的一間出租屋內玩微信。他使用已故恐怖組織阿蓋德領袖拉登的照片作為頭像，在群組與他人聊天，有群組成員看見後就稱「看，大人物來了」，張強接着就順勢回了一句「跟我加入ISIS」。<br />\n<br />\n約一個月後，北京昌平區警方就傳喚張強到案，指他涉嫌宣揚恐怖主義、極端主義。案件今年6月中旬在北京第一中院審結宣判，法官認定張強法制觀念淡薄，在該個有300多人的聊天群組中宣揚恐怖主義、極端主義，情節嚴重，重判有期徒刑9個月、罰款1000元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該係有人督灰<br />\n否則就咁講一句, 公安鬼知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27109d1ab2780169e524c872996ddf8bf7dc032","tid":412139,"uid":62532,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"鄰國wechat有完善既反恐系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c96bf10c48e857896a3c0f7297cb3d50428c36","tid":412139,"uid":54876,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"用微信同直駁公安局有咩分別"},{"pid":"1ab1b8115b4caf31bd688daf4093b7ac629b846c","tid":412139,"uid":35014,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:41:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f10b9a0274dc017c1c70731c782bbe13b3608360","tid":412139,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用微信同直駁公安局有咩分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公安咁得閒, 每日睇幾十億條 對話??"